- [x] Run database migration script
- [ ] Test all table relationships and constraints

### Backend API Routes
- [x] Create `/api/module-creator/modules` endpoints
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/modules - List all modules
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/modules/:id - Get single module
  - [x] POST /api/module-creator/modules - Create new module
  - [x] PUT /api/module-creator/modules/:id - Update module
  - [x] DELETE /api/module-creator/modules/:id - Delete module
- [x] Create `/api/module-creator/submodules` endpoints
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/modules/:moduleId/submodules - List submodules
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/submodules/:id - Get single submodule
  - [x] POST /api/module-creator/modules/:moduleId/submodules - Create submodule
  - [x] PUT /api/module-creator/submodules/:id - Update submodule
  - [x] DELETE /api/module-creator/submodules/:id - Delete submodule
  - [x] PUT /api/module-creator/submodules/reorder - Reorder submodules
- [x] Create `/api/module-creator/media` endpoints
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/media - List media assets
  - [x] POST /api/module-creator/media/upload - Upload media file
  - [x] DELETE /api/module-creator/media/:id - Delete media asset
  - [x] GET /api/module-creator/media/:id/thumbnail - Get thumbnail
- [x] Add authentication middleware for admin routes
- [x] Add file upload middleware (Multer)
- [x] Add error handling middleware

